The '''Looking for America Tour''' was a concert tour by American alternative rock bands [[Switchfoot]] and [[Relient K]] in support of their albums ''[[Where the Light Shines Through]]'' and ''[[Air for Free]]''.<ref>{{cite web|title=Concert Spotlight: SWITCHFOOT Announces Tour With RELIENT K|url=http://latfusa.com/article/2016/5/concert-spotlight-switchfoot-announces-tour-with/|website=LATF USA|publisher=LATF USA|accessdate=May 16, 2016|date=May 16, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Switchfoot and Relient K Announce Fall 2016 "Looking for America Tour"|url=http://musicexistence.com/blog/2016/05/16/switchfoot-relient-k-announce-fall-2016-looking-for-america-tour/|website=Music Existence|publisher=Music Existence|accessdate=May 16, 2016|date=May 16, 2016}}</ref> The co-headlining tour spanned 44 dates across the United States from September through November 2016.<ref>{{cite web|last1=Sharp|first1=Tyler|title=Switchfoot, Relient K announce co-headlining tour|url=http://www.altpress.com/news/entry/switchfoot_relient_k_announce_co_headlining_tour|website=[[Alternative Press (music magazine)|Alternative Press]]|publisher=[[Alternative Press (music magazine)|Alternative Press]]|accessdate=May 16, 2016|date=May 16, 2016}}</ref>

