{{italic title}} '''''Read.''''' is a [[Tabloid (newspaper format)|tabloid]]-sized weekly [[magazine]] with a newspaper approach that is distributed to [[commuter]]s in the [[Dubai Metro]] network.<ref>[http://www.thenational.ae/business/media/read-all-about-it-aboard-the-dubai-metro Read all about it aboard the Dubai Metro]; by Ben Flanagan; in ''[[The National (Abu Dhabi)|The National]]''; published June 20, 2011; retrieved July 3 2011</ref>
''Read.'' is the first publication in the [[Middle East]] region produced exclusively for metro commuters. ''Read.'' is published in English and it is available free of charge.
